OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying
OL,6,Fcloudy in the evening with showers
OL,7,Fexpected across Kent, easing off into
OL,8,Fthe early hours. Elsewhere drier, with
OL,9,Fclear skies allowing a rural frost to
OL,10,Fdevelop.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FVariable cloud, with sunny
OL,13,Fspells and a risk of showers through
OL,14,Fthe day. Temperatures higher than
OL,15,FWednesday, but feeling cooler along
OL,16,Fthe coast where there is a stronger
OL,17,Fbreeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
