OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFriday
OL,6,Fbrings sunny spells and scattered
OL,7,Fshowers. Rain or showers, occasionally
OL,8,Fheavy, are likely on Saturday at some
OL,9,Fpoint. Sunday appears drier away from
OL,10,Fsouthern coasts, where heavy showers
OL,11,Fpossible.
